					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10035872#post-4143296</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10035872/scp-3583#post-4143296</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 06 Feb 2019 03:16:42 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Rounderhouse</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4187885</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Good stuff, just a few minor nitpicks.</p> <blockquote> <p>As well, close inspection reveals that it is composed of a wide variety of mismatched schoolbus parts, held together by an unknown force.</p> </blockquote> <p>Kind of odd to start the sentence off with &quot;As well&quot;, might be beneficial to change that to &quot;In addition&quot;.</p> <blockquote> <p>…that son</p> </blockquote> <p>Should be a space just before &quot;that&quot;, I think.</p> <p>But yeah, amusing skip, and it's quite refreshing to see realistic dialogue and civilians in a skip.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
