					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10035872#post-4126406</guid>
				<title>Explanation</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10035872/scp-3583#post-4126406</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 21 Jan 2019 19:40:35 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Voct</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>392303</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It's a demon.</p> <p>But it thinks it's a schoolbus.</p> <p>So it does schoolbus things.</p> <p>But it's still a demon.</p> <p>So it does them in a demonic way.</p> <p>This SCP was inspired by the &quot;schoolbus that compels kids to get on board and then you can see a hell dimension out the windows and also many of the kids disappear&quot; SCP that was posted just over a year ago by Leveritas.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
